rows.label: tev006301_MSG0001
rows.name:
Our sickened brethren and children will survive
thanks to the medicines you humans shared.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev006301_MSG0003
rows.name:
If there is aught I can do to repay this kindness,
I beg you to ask it of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev006301_MSG0004
rows.name:
In all the campaigns I have fought,
I have never met a people as strong as yours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev006301_MSG0005
rows.name:
I yearn for an opportunity to fight alongside your
species again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev006301_MSG0006
rows.name:
I hope there is a way for we Wrothians to maintain
both our alliance and our rivalry with humanity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev006301_MSG0007
rows.name:
For our species would surely drive each other to levels
of military prowess far beyond what we can even
imagine today![ST:wait ]
